Paper: hep-th/0106086

Date: 2001-06-11

Title: Friedmann equation and Cardy formula correspondence in brane universes

Authors: Bin Wang, Elcio Abdalla and Ru-Keng Su

Comments: latex file, 11 pages

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A17 (2002) 23-30

We study the brane with arbitrary tension $\sigma$ on the edge of variousblack holes with AdS asymptotics. We investigate Friedmann equations governingthe motion of the brane universes and match the Friedmann equation to Cardyentropy formula.